Author: Updating,
Description: In the chaotic period of the Republic of China, Chen Qiming, an opera actor in Peking Opera Association, was entangled by a new warlord, Yan Ci, at the first sight. Circulating between the support and threat of warlord forces, involving in the competition and grudges of opera association, Chen Qiming gradually found another side of Yan Ci under his military uniform. Who would have thought that the enmity between them had begun from childhood, and destined by this chaotic period.
